<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/18789036-the-expeditions"><img alt="The Expeditions: An Early Biography of Muḥammad" style="height: 75px;" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1384735404l/18789036._SY75_.jpg" />
