<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/21927609-two-arabic-travel-books"><img alt="Two Arabic Travel Books: Accounts of China and India and Mission to the Volga" style="height: 75px;" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1402326284l/21927609._SY75_.jpg" />
